languages.text: "Прелестно, теперь мы в гостях у фанатиков. Шерин, поищем безопасное местечко, где не воняет кровью?"
"So, our gracious hosts are a cult of fanatics. How delightful. Shereen, could we perhaps look for a safe place that smells of something other than blood?"

languages.text: « Donc si je comprends bien, nos gracieux hôtes appartiennent en réalité à un culte de fanatiques. Comme c'est amusant. Et si nous cherchions un endroit sûr qui n'empeste pas le sang, shereen ? »
languages.original_text: "So, our gracious hosts are a cult of fanatics. How delightful. Shereen, could we perhaps look for a safe place that smells of something other than blood?"

languages.text: «Así que nuestros amables anfitriones son un culto de fanáticos. Encantador. Shereen, ¿podríamos buscar un refugio que apeste menos a sangre?».

languages.text: 「つまり、私たちのご親切なホストはカルトの狂信者なのですね。素晴らしい。シェリーン、血の匂いのしない安全な場所を探すことはできない？」
languages.original_text: "So, our gracious hosts are a cult of fanatics. How delightful. Shereen, could we perhaps look for a safe place that smells of something other than blood?"

traits.locale_text: 「つまり、私たちのご親切なホストはカルトの狂信者なのですね。素晴らしい。シャリーン、血の匂いのしない安全な場所を探すことはできない？」

languages.text: “也就是说，招待我们的人是一群狂热分子，这实在是太令人愉悦了。亲爱的，我们能不能找个没有血味的安全之处？”
languages.original_text: "So, our gracious hosts are a cult of fanatics. How delightful. Shereen, could we perhaps look for a safe place that smells of something other than blood?"

languages.text: "Yani nazik ev sahiplerimiz, fanatiklerden oluşan bir tarikat çıktı. Ne hoş. Şirinim, belki de kan dışında herhangi bir kokunun hâkim olduğu güvenli bir yer arayabiliriz."
languages.original_text: "So, our gracious hosts are a cult of fanatics. How delightful. Shereen, could we perhaps look for a safe place that smells of something other than blood?"
